definition.value: Mixture of chemicals and/or extracts formulated in such a way to reproduce the original Muscat grapes flavour. The effect is generally intense, therefore small amounts are able to provide a well recognisable smell and taste to the food to which it is added.[https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Flavor]
